    <learningContentbody>
        <lcInstruction>
            <p>The final element in a &lt;taskbody> element is the postrequisites (&lt;postreq>)
                element. </p>
            <p>Use the &lt;postreq> element to document the things that the reader must do once the
                task is complete. Examples include:</p>
            <ul id="ul_hj2_wbq_bt">
                <li>Putting equipment away or closing files</li>
                <li>Documenting or logging the task completion</li>
                <li>Performing subsequent tasks </li>
            </ul>
        </lcInstruction>
    </learningContentbody>
